orie ein neues Themengebiet von großer gesellschaftlicher Bedeutung.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aGesellschaft. 4aGesellschaftstheorie. 4aKörper. 4aModerne Gesellschaft. 4aSoziologie. 4aSystemtheorie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh  aBody.  aSociety.  aSociology.  aSystems Theory.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2000-2009z9783110463415oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Sozialw. 2000-2009z9783110463392oZDB-23-TSW0 cprintz978389942210840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839402108?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839402108423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839402108/original  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2000d2009  aZDB-23-TSWc2000d2009